snippet.title: Orcs Must Die! 3 - Tipping the Scales DLC - Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description: The new Orcs Must Die 3! DLC, Tipping the Scales, is now available! It comes with five new maps (including a war scenario), a new desert biome, the new Tuatara Race, new gear, new skins, and plenty more!
